HEADWORD: Zoonomy
<hw>Zo*on"o*my</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Zoo-</ets> +
Gr. <?/ a law: cf. F. <ets>zoonomie</ets>.]</ety> <def>The laws of
animal life, or the science which treats of the phenomena of animal
life, their causes and relations.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

